item.description: My 2nd "official" Genesis Child Theme FreelancePro is built for the creative freelancer. Perfect for web designers, web developers, photographers, graphic designers and more...but flexible enough to use for any industry. It comes packaged with Advanced Custom Fields PRO and has a ready-to-use page builder to create dynamic layouts in minutes.
item.content:encoded: My 2nd “official” Genesis Child Theme FreelancePro is built for the creative freelancer. Perfect for web designers, web developers, photographers, graphic designers and more…but flexible enough to use for any industry. It comes packaged with Advanced Custom Fields PRO and has a ready-to-use page builder to create dynamic layouts in minutes.
